Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:03.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキハラハラ こんなのはじめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:06.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこまで私の 気持ちをもてあそぶの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視無視ムリムリ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然始まる 大スペクタクル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっと言わせる為に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:16.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すべてを 賭けてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每日 大迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:23.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お気楽マイペース男の子！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:28.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,とぼけた顔してもダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:31.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對大迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:33.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど つい見ちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:38.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君のこと 気になって！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:42.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今度は何にするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:42.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:03.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}緊張兮兮 神經兮兮 從來沒試過這種感受的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:06.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你要玩弄人家的感情到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}無視無視 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}突然開始的大奇觀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}動員自己的一切腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:16.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}就是為了讓我大喊一聲「啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}每天都搞怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:23.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你這個不安分又特立獨行的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:28.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}一臉無辜的表情也是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:31.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}絕對在搞怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:33.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不過又忍不住看過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:42.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}好在意 你這次又搞什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:42.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不要啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天參加林間學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是遠足的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分組沿著山路朝著展望台行進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的小組在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成員是這六人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 關君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在空氣這麼清新的自然環境裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼煩惱都變得不值一提了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天不是在教室裏 放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}魔王的城堡 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王的城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(484,530)\shad0\bord0\c&H1F2123&}林間學校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王的城堡是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還寫著危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫這個的連小學生都不如吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來剛才住宿處的職員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來很眼熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候在這裏住過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的作品有好好留下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個惡作劇小孩長大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還自稱過魔王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼樣的小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然聽到了這樣的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是關君以前做的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真夠難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有點看不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位停一停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會落後其他組的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐立不安是因為這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那確實會在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 又有了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊 池子那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沸騰沼澤 只要沾到這裏的水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會受到燙傷的詛咒而死 ——魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個寫的很當真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要好好打掩護才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊 笑成這樣 製作的人很可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候不論誰都會有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫魔王說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫井真溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那眼神 我的好感度上升了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被當成維護小朋友的溫柔的人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是當著被人狂笑的本人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很尷尬而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤解了被他感謝也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常老讓我那麼頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快來看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又發現很厲害的東西了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍 龍的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前的騎士用屠龍刀打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愛惜自然的話會復活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屠龍刀是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 關君極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個墳墓裏會埋著什麼麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇澤君 你別多手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 找到屠龍刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還真挖出來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用尺子做的屠龍刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們笑過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被懷疑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太過在意關君的眼神了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:06:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實我是太過維護未曾謀面的小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家笑成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一點也沒反應也確實可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道關君在懷疑我已經注意到了魔王的真身就是關君嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要 尷尬得想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好一直裝作什麼都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要自然點 自然點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要自然點 自然點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼有點消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這一段是撐過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏好像也有什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是迷茫森林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠地彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對出不去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接寫上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們進迷茫森林了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不會迷路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的一條大路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要迷路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還有點可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 關君耳朵都通紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 關君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關君 不是那裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果那個寫警告的人開始迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有柱子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這些東西居然沒被撤掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來到魔王的城堡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 發現城堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王的城堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 最後的城堡是這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是平面的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用油漆畫在板上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿滿的手工感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關君覺得很滿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來關君不是討厭兒時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是討厭低水平的製作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這繩子什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 解開來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然很危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背面是失敗過一次的畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}幹的漂亮 I名字is關俊成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是通關獎勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿自製的畫做獎勵 你究竟有多自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還上框了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且關君還寫著名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要被人看到的話 就是個超級難為情炸彈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要藏起來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這麼大的畫框放不進我的背包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該 該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 有點走累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達 展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊完全沒心情享受景色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來路上看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們組也爆笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王的城堡也超搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大家都知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西得快點丟到沒人注意的地方纔行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一臉清爽地吹什麼風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一個人擺什麼「全都是小時候的事情啊」的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別丟下我 自己一個人解放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這是關君的恥辱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我是無關的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要這麼辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小河
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 丟到那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 剛才有條大魚跳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 去抓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連關君都上了啊 白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連條小魚都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生真是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沸騰沼澤真是傑作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來差不多就是那池子的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流到這邊的池子來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫井
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒啥 只是洗下手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 那個池子會燙傷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西帶回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關君還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的命運已經被新的魔王所掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課小動作

